Zucchini Pizza Bites with Mozzarella

$8.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

AppetizerHealthyLow-Carb

Description

Crispy zucchini rounds topped with melted mozzarella and savory marinara sauce, perfect for a healthy snack!

Ingredients

  • Zucchini: 2 medium
  • Mozzarella Cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • Marinara Sauce: 1/2 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Italian Seasoning: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
